	(684,344,'_seo_cached_filtered__content_new','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-900\" title=\"student education games\" alt=\"student education games\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/student.png\" width=\"342\" height=\"348\" /></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n[two_third]<strong>Tired of boring tests to take in school?</strong> Why cant it be more fun and in a game? Finally Class Compete will give you that. Look through our list of Challenges, play the game and see how you do. Get your friends involved and you can compete against them. Earn coins, Customize your Character make them dance![/two_third][one_third_last][button icon=\" icon-user\" size=\"large\" type=\"primary\" value=\" &gt; Join ClassCompete Now! \" title=\"Join/Login ClassCompete\" href=\"http://student.classcompete.com\"]\n\n[/one_third_last]&nbsp;\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-cloud-download\"]  <span style=\"color: #993300;\">D</span>ownload the App</h2>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 90px;\">It is easy to be part of the action. Download the software from the App store, or login from our website. When you enter the software, you will be asked for a class code provided by your teacher. Get ready....its going to be fun!!!</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-group\"]  <span style=\"color: #993300;\">P</span>lay with your Classmates</h2>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 90px;\">When you are in your classroom, your teacher will assign you challenges to play. Challenges are simply competitions where you can compete against your classmates. Its a battle of skill AND knowledge.</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-dashboard\"]  <span style=\"color: #993300;\">S</span>ee your Results</h2>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 90px;\">With Class Compete you get to see how you compare against your classmates! While playing you will earn valuable coins where you can customize your characters, animate your character in cool ways and much more. As you perform better you will see more items become available to you.</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-trophy\"]  <span style=\"color: #993300;\">E</span>arn Points and Become a Star!!!</h2>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 90px;\">The more you play the more you can make your character stand out from the rest, different rounds show your characters in their different looks and their animations you earned. You can be the star of the classroom in so many ways!!!</p>\n&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[button icon=\" icon-user\" size=\"large\" type=\"primary\" value=\" &gt; Join ClassCompete Now! \" title=\"Join/Login ClassCompete\" href=\"http://student.classcompete.com\"]</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Educational games made simple and FUN - Class Compete! [icon name=\"icon-thumbs-up\"]</h2>'),
