	(1748,684,'_seo_cached_filtered__content_new','[buttons-toolbar][/buttons-toolbar]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[service]<br class=\"nc\" />[icon name=\"icon-thumbs-up\"]\r\n<h2>Service title</h2>\r\nService content\r\n\r\n[/service]<br class=\"nc\" />[tabs]<br class=\"nc\" />[thead]<br class=\"nc\" />[tab class=\"active\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_first_tab41\" title=\"CHALLENGES- Step 1\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[tab class=\"\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_tab137821068352341\" title=\"LOGIN &amp; PLAY - Step 2\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[tab class=\"\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_tab137821096119441\" title=\"MEASURE - Step 3\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[/thead][tcontents]<br class=\"nc\" />[tcontent class=\"active\" id=\"dnp_first_tab41\"]Challenges are topic based assessments organized by grade and subject. One can view challenges that are already built and found in our marketplace and select them to be used in your competition. If you do not see one that fits your academic need, then use our content builder in the teacher portal and create your own! [/tcontent]<br class=\"nc\" />[tcontent class=\"\" id=\"dnp_tab137821068352341\"]Our assessment environment is built in unique 3-D game that appeals to visual, auditory and tactile learners. In short, it looks cool, sounds great and makes you engage on screen in different ways, while being tested the entire time. For convenience, It works on an Ipad, Android or regular desktop computer. Simply login to our system and compete with your classmates and see how your rate. Along the way collect coins and other items that allow you to customize your character, change music and win prizes. Lets go! [/tcontent]<br class=\"nc\" />[tcontent class=\"\" id=\"dnp_tab137821096119441\"]Our system provides assessment data in real-time. Your character earns credits to purchase items in the game to increase their characters appearance and environmental factors, but most importantly you can see immediately how you compare against your classmates, your schoolmates, and others in the country. Its interesting information for parents and teachers alike! [/tcontent]<br class=\"nc\" />[/tcontents]<br class=\"nc\" />[/tabs]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">[collapse id=\"collapse_45\" class=\"\"]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[citem title=\"</span><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>Collapsible Group Item 1</strong></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">\" id=\"citem_19\" parent=\"collapse_45\"]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Collapsible item 1 content goes here..</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[/citem]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[citem title=\"Collapsible Group Item 2\" id=\"citem_84\" parent=\"collapse_45\"]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Collapsible item 2 content goes here..</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[/citem]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[citem title=\"Collapsible Group Item 3\" id=\"citem_58\" parent=\"collapse_45\"]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Collapsible item 3 content goes here..</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[/citem]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"color: #000000;\">[/collapse]</span>\r\n\r\n[collapse id=\"collapse_79\" class=\"\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[citem title=\"<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Challenge</span>\" id=\"citem_38\" parent=\"collapse_79\"]<br class=\"nc\" />Challenges are topic based assessments organized by grade and subjet. View challenges that are built already in our marketplace. If you do not see one, then use our content builder in the teacher portal and create your own!<br class=\"nc\" />[/citem]<br class=\"nc\" />[citem title=\"<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Play</span></span>!\" id=\"citem_82\" parent=\"collapse_79\"]<br class=\"nc\" />Our gaming environment is built in 3-D in a way that appeals to visual, auditory and tactile learners. In short, it looks cool, has great sounds and makes you engage on screen while being tested the whole time. It works on an Ipad, Android or regular desktop computer. Its simply a fun way to practice test on any device. <br class=\"nc\" />[/citem]<br class=\"nc\" />[citem title=\"Measure\" id=\"citem_87\" parent=\"collapse_79\"]<br class=\"nc\" />Our system provides data in real-time. The character earns credits to purchase items in the game to increase their characters appearance and environmental factors, but most importantly you can see immediately how you compare against your classmates, your schoolmates, and others in the country. Its really interesting information for parents and teachers alike!<br class=\"nc\" />[/citem]<br class=\"nc\" />[/collapse]'),
