	(1992,726,'_seo_cached_filtered__content_new','<p>When creating our gaming platform we knew it would \"take a village\" to raise this child! Below are some of the partners who have helped us be successful. We thank them for their past, present and future efforts to make Class Compete be the best academic gaming platform possible. They believe in our unique vision and we hope you will as well.</p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\"><img title=\"\" class=\"size-full wp-image-734 aligncenter\" alt=\"Learn It Systems\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/learnitlogo.jpg\" width=\"294\" height=\"62\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">www.learnitsystems.com</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: left;\">Learn It is an educational organization dedicated to ensuring every student succeeds in schooland life by delivering fresh, practical programs to support improved school performance.Throughacademic, enrichment, and special education solutions, our team of education professionals worksto create exceptional learning experiences for children inside and outside of the classroom.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><img title=\"\" class=\"size-full wp-image-735 aligncenter\" alt=\"sunsetrecords\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/sunsetrecords.jpg\" width=\"244\" height=\"167\" />  www.sunsetentertainmentgroup.com</td>\n<td>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Sunset Entertainment Group is an independent entertainment company that specializes in the development and management of artists, producers, songwriters, engineers, and the marketing, licensing, production, and distribution of music by these talented individuals. Since its inception in July 1998, Sunset has forged ahead creating a new path for its one of a kind goal and attitude. Sunset Music Group in conjunction with Sunset Entertainment Group (SEG) strives to combine all ethnic backgrounds with various musical styles yielding unique artists set to expose the world to their new flavors.Sunsets team has unparalleled relationships and networks within the music and entertainment industries, that few can compare to.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Clients include: ASHANTI -ASHLEE SIMPSON -BRITNEY SPEARS -CHERYL COLE -CHRIS CORNELL -CRAIG DAVID -DANITY KANE -DAY 26 -DEMI LOVATO -DIMA BILAN -DURAN DURAN -FANTASIA -JAMIE FOXX -JENNIFER HUDSON -JOE JONAS -KATHERINE MCPHEE -KERI HILSON -KEYSHIA COLE -NELLY FURTADO -P. DIDDY -PUSSYCAT DOLLS -SHAKIRA -TIMBALAND</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n'),
