	(83,1,'2013-04-15 16:00:44','2013-04-15 16:00:44','[row class=\"row-fluid\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>Gamification of Testing to Improve Scores[icon name=\"icon-lightbulb\"]</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333333;\">1) 3- D gaming environment kids LOVE.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333333;\">2) Play challenges ( sample tests)</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333333;\">3) Compete against classmates. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333333;\">4) Teachers &amp; Parents get instant performance results to make decisions.</span>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333333;\">... Focus on NEW Common Core Curriculum</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: #333333;\"><strong>... Test Scores Improvement- Just 5 min a day is all it takes!</strong>\r\n</span></p>\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>100,000 children tested...survey says?  [icon name=\"icon-bar-chart\"]</h3>\r\nUsing 3 styles of tutoring, 100,000 children* in grades 2-8 were instructed. Test scores were compared from before tutoring and after. The results are clear: students performance can improve with technology and testing.\r\n\r\n[progress value=88 text=\'Teacher PLUS Technology:     <em>8.68 pts</em>\'][progress value=70 text=\'Online Teacher:             <em>7.23 pts</em>\'][progress value=55 text=\'Teacher:   <em>5.62 pts</em>\']\r\n\r\n<i>*Data provided by Learn It Systems- 20 hours of math tutoring 2010-2013</i>\r\n\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]\r\n\r\n[team]\r\n\r\n<hr style=\"width: 1px;\" width=\"1\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">More About Us !!!</h1>\r\n\r\n<hr style=\"width: 1px;\" width=\"1\" />\r\n\r\n[bloglist]','The Idea','','publish','open','open','','the-idea','','','2013-12-26 16:45:47','2013-12-26 20:45:47','',0,'http://themestrong.com/demo/a