	(308,1,'2013-05-17 01:34:07','2013-05-17 05:34:07','[row class=\"row-fluid\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>WHAT WE DO</h3>\r\nWe are an experienced group of professionals that have been involved in education for over 20 years. In this time we have seen the educational process can be broken into 4 distinct pieces: Gathering Data, Teaching, [Testing], and Application. In our experience the testing piece has evolved the least over the years. Bubble Sheets? Really? Mobile technology has changed the paradigm of education. Students should be able to compare themselves against others instantly, not wait for test results to come back. We aim to merge interactive gaming, testing, competition with mobile technologies. Step up and take a challenge We ARE.. Class Compete! \r\n\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>DATA DATA DATA</h3>\r\nWe studied 90,000 children from 2010-2013 where supplemental educational services were provided to students 2-8th grades using 3 types of math tutoring. Improvements were measured via pre and post tutoring tests. The results*\r\n[progress value=80 text=\'Traditional Teacher  5.62\'][progress value=90 text=\'Teacher PLUS Technology  8.68\'][progress value=60 text=\'Online Teacher  7.23\']\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]\r\n[row class=\"row-fluid\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>EDUCATORS</h3>\r\nYou know each students learns differently. How can you check if they understand what you are teaching? Class Compete gives you a testing platform to get instant results and appealing to all learning types. Students engage using a 3-D gaming environment playing any challenge you assign to them. It will work on Tablets as well as Desktops and Laptops. Its simple. You setup a classroom then assign a challenge that is aligned to a subject matter and let them play! You instantly get the results and see how they compare against each other and different classrooms around the country.\r\n<h3>PARENTS</h3>\r\nYour students are in the most competitive time in history. The world has become flat. Content is produced all over the world and available instantly to anyone. Students have access to more information than when you grew up and also have more pressure to compete in this global environment. How do you give your student a better chance? Do you know how they compare against the rest of the world? Do you even know how they compare against kids in their classroom today? Class Compete gives your students the opportunity to use tablet technology, creative new testing styles and compete against others in their classroom and the world. The best part is you will know instantly how they compare. Want to see? Sign them up now!\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>STUDENTS</h3>\r\nTired of boring tests to take in school or at work? Why cant it be more fun and in a game so it cool? Finally Class Compete will give you that. Look through our list of Challenges, play the game and see how you do. Get your friends involved and you can compete against them. Earn coins, Customize your Characteryou can even make them dance!\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','The Idea','','inherit','open','open','','83-revision-v1','','','2013-05-17 01:34:07','2013-05-17 05:34:07','',83,'http://classcompete.com/308',0,'revision','',0),
