.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-trophy\"]  <span style=\"color: #993300;\">E</span>arn Points and Become a Star!!!</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 90px;\">The more you play the more you can make your character stand out from the rest, different rounds show your characters in their different looks and their animations you earned. You can be the star of the classroom in so many ways!!!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[button icon=\" icon-user\" size=\"large\" type=\"primary\" value=\" &gt; Join ClassCompete Now! \" title=\"Join/Login ClassCompete\" href=\"http://student.classcompete.com\"]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Educational games made simple and FUN - Class Compete! [icon name=\"icon-thumbs-up\"]</h2>','Student Information','','publish','open','open','','student_information','','','2014-01-04 13:31:31','2014-01-04 17:31:31','',0,'http://www.classcompete.com/?page_id=344',0,'page','',0),
