sts sent more than once in a calendar year, or requests submitted to an address other than the one posted in this notice. Please note that this law does not cover all information sharing. Our disclosure only includes information covered by the law.\n\r\n<b>Contact Information<br />\n</b>If you have any questions or suggestions regarding our Privacy Policy, please contact us via e-mail at privacy @ classcompete.com.\n\r\n&nbsp;\n\r\n&nbsp;\n\r\n','Privacy Policy','','publish','open','open','','privacy','','','2013-08-15 16:38:28','2013-08-15 20:38:28','',0,'http://www.classcompete.com/?page_id=519',0,'page','',0),
