	(529,1,'2013-06-03 00:59:18','2013-06-03 04:59:18','[row class=\"row-fluid\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\n\r\n<h3>WHAT WE DO  [icon name=\"icon-lightbulb\"]</h3>\nWe are an experienced group of professionals that have been involved in education for over 20 years. In this time we have seen the educational process can be broken into 4 distinct pieces: Gathering Data, Teaching, [Testing], and Application. In our experience the testing piece has evolved the least over the years. Bubble Sheets? Really? Mobile technology has changed the paradigm of education. Students should be able to compare themselves against others instantly, not wait for test results to come back. We aim to merge interactive gaming, testing, competition with mobile technologies. Step up and take a challenge We ARE.. Class Compete!\n\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\n\r\n<h3>DATA DATA DATA  [icon name=\"icon-bar-chart\"]</h3>\nWe studied 90,000 children from 2010-2013 where supplemental educational services were provided to students 2\'nd to 8\'th grades using 3 styles of math tutoring. Improvements were measured via pre and post tutoring tests with average point gains shown below.* The results are clear: students are relating to cool new technology more than ever before.<br />\n[progress value=56 text=\'Traditional Teacher:     <em>5.62 pts</em>\'][progress value=87 text=\'Teacher PLUS Technology:     <em>8.68 pts</em>\'][progress value=72 text=\'Online Teacher:             <em>7.23 pts</em>\']<br />\n<i>*Data provided by Learn It Systems</i><br />\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]<br />\n[team]\n\r\n','The Idea','','inherit','open','open','','83-revision-v1','','','2013-06-03 00:59:18','2013-06-03 04:59:18','',83,'http://www.classcompete.com/529',0,'revision','',0),
