	(605,1,'2013-08-16 17:41:02','2013-08-16 21:41:02','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">[row class=\"row-fluid\"]</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\">Problem Solving Skills</span> [icon name=\"icon-group\"][/col]</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"color: #993300;\">Encourage Creativity</span> [icon name=\"icon-refresh icon-spin\"][/col]</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"color: #000080;\">Test Prep-Easy for You</span> [icon name=\"icon-check\"][/col]</span></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"color: #993300;\">Happy Kids!</span> <img title=\"Ha Ha\" alt=\"Ha Ha\" src=\"/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-tinymce/addons/emotions/img/popobig/haha.png\" border=\"0\" />[/col]</span><br class=\"nc\" /><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">[/row]</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<hr style=\"width: 1000px;\" width=\"1000\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-bolt\"] <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #993300;\">E</span>ducational Games - Give Your Kids an Advantage ?</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Young learners today are being consumed by the convergence of technology with education. <strong>Educational Games</strong> and technology are part of their world more then ever. As technology becomes more accessible through phones, mobile consoles, gaming devices, laptops and tablets, there is a massive potential to give your student the upper hand advantage in comparison to other students. Give them the right tools and you can Imp