	(691,1,'2013-09-03 09:31:02','2013-09-03 13:31:02','[row class=\"row-fluid\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>What We Do  [icon name=\"icon-lightbulb\"]</h3>\r\n[tabs]\r\n[thead]\r\n[tab class=\"active\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_first_tab41\" title=\"CHALLENGES &gt;\"]\r\n[tab class=\"\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_tab137821068352341\" title=\"LOGIN &amp; PLAY &gt;\"]\r\n[tab class=\"\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_tab137821096119441\" title=\"MEASURE \"]\r\n[/thead][tcontents]\r\n[tcontent class=\"active\" id=\"dnp_first_tab41\"]Challenges are topic based assessments organized by grade and subject. One can view challenges that are already built and found in our marketplace and select them to be used in your competition. If you do not see one that fits your academic need, then use our content builder in the teacher portal and create your own! [/tcontent]\r\n[tcontent class=\"\" id=\"dnp_tab137821068352341\"]Our assessment environment is built in unique 3-D game that appeals to visual, auditory and tactile learners. In short, it looks cool, sounds great and makes you engage on screen in different ways, while being tested the entire time. For convenience, It works on an Ipad, Android or regular desktop computer. Simply login to our system and compete with your classmates and see how your rate. Along the way collect coins and other items that allow you to customize your character, change music and win prizes. Lets go! [/tcontent]\r\n[tcontent class=\"\" id=\"dnp_tab137821096119441\"]Our system provides assessment data in real-time. Your character earns credits to purchase items in the game to increase their characters appearance and environmental factors, but most importantly you can see immediately how you compare against your classmates, your schoolmates, and others in the country. Its interesting information for parents and teachers alike! [/tcontent]\r\n[/tcontents]\r\n[/tabs]\r\n\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>Data... Data... Data...  [icon name=\"icon-bar-chart\"]</h3>\r\nWe studied 90,000 children from 2010-2013 where supplemental educational services were provided to students 2\'nd to 8\'th grades using 3 styles of math tutoring. Improvements were measured via pre and post tutoring tests with average point gains shown below.* The results are clear: students are relating to cool new technology more than ever before.\r\n\r\n[progress value=88 text=\'Teacher PLUS Technology:     <em>8.68 pts</em>\'][progress value=70 text=\'Online Teacher:             <em>7.23 pts</em>\'][progress value=55 text=\'Teacher:   <em>5.62 pts</em>\']\r\n\r\n<i>*Data provided by Learn It Systems</i>\r\n\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]\r\n\r\n[team]','The Idea','','inherit','open','open','','83-revision-v1','','','2013-09-03 09:31:02','2013-09-03 13:31:02','',83,'http://www.classcompete.com/691',0,'revision','',0),
