	(751,1,'2013-09-06 21:26:43','2013-09-07 01:26:43','[row class=\"row-fluid\"]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>What We Do  [icon name=\"icon-lightbulb\"]</h3>\r\n[tabs]\r\n[thead]\r\n[tab class=\"active\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_first_tab41\" title=\"CHALLENGES &gt;\"]\r\n[tab class=\"\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_tab137821068352341\" title=\"LOGIN &amp; PLAY &gt;\"]\r\n[tab class=\"\" type=\"tab\" href=\"#dnp_tab137821096119441\" title=\"MEASURE \"]\r\n[/thead][tcontents]\r\n[tcontent class=\"active\" id=\"dnp_first_tab41\"]Challenges are topic based assessments organized by grade and subject. One can view challenges that are already built and found in our marketplace and select them to be used in your competition. If you do not see one that fits your academic need, then use our content builder in the teacher portal and create your own! [/tcontent]\r\n[tcontent class=\"\" id=\"dnp_tab137821068352341\"]Our assessment environment is built in unique 3-D game that appeals to visual, auditory and tactile learners. In short, it looks cool, sounds great and makes you engage on screen in different ways, while being tested the entire time. For convenience, It works on an Ipad, Android or regular desktop computer. Simply login to our system and compete with your classmates and see how your rate. Along the way collect coins and other items that allow you to customize your character, change music and win prizes. Lets go! [/tcontent]\r\n[tcontent class=\"\" id=\"dnp_tab137821096119441\"]Our system provides assessment data in real-time. Your character earns credits to purchase items in the game to increase their characters appearance and environmental factors, but most importantly you can see immediately how you compare against your classmates, your schoolmates, and others in the country. Its interesting information for parents and teachers alike! [/tcontent]\r\n[/tcontents]\r\n[/tabs]\r\n\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span6\"]\r\n<h3>Data... Data... Data...  [icon name=\"icon-bar-chart\"]</h3>\r\nWe studied 100,000 children from 2010-2013 where supplemental educational services were provided to students 2\'nd to 8\'th grades using 3 styles of math tutoring. Improvements were measured via pre and post tutoring tests with average point gains shown below.* The results are clear: students are relating to cool new technology more than ever before.\r\n\r\n[progress value=88 text=\'Teacher PLUS Technology:     <em>8.68 pts</em>\'][progress value=70 text=\'Online Teacher:             <em>7.23 pts</em>\'][progress value=55 text=\'Teacher:   <em>5.62 pts</em>\']\r\n\r\n<i>*Data provided by Learn It Systems</i>\r\n\r\n[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]\r\n\r\n[team]','The Idea','','inherit','closed','closed','','83-revision-v1','','','2013-09-06 21:26:43','2013-09-07 01:26:43','',83,'http://www.classcompete.com/83-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(752,1,'2013-09-06 21:27:16','2013-09-07 01:27:16','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">[row class=\"row-fluid\"]</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">[col class=\"span3\"]Problem Solving Skills [icon name=\"icon-group\"][/col]</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"color: #993300;\">Encourage Creativity</span> [icon name=\"icon-globe\"][/col]</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span3\"]Test Prep-Easy for You [icon name=\"icon-check\"][/col]</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br class=\"nc\" />[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"color: #993300;\">Happy Kids!</span> <img title=\"Ha Ha\" alt=\"Ha Ha\" src=\"/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-tinymce/addons/emotions/img/popobig/haha.png\" border=\"0\" />[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-bolt\"] <span style=\"color: #993300;\">E</span>ducational Games - Give Your Kids an Advantage ?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Young learners today are being consumed by the convergence of technology with education. <strong>Educational Games</strong> and technology are part of their world more then ever. As technology becomes more accessible through phones, mobile consoles, gaming devices, laptops and tablets, there is a massive potential to give your student the upper hand advantage in comparison to other students. Give them the right tools and you can Improve Student Performance.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">A recent report on Elementary Educational Games andEducational Games for Teens<strong></strong>was produced in March of 2013. This report was funded by the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation and carried out by SRI International. The research examined 77 studies that were conducted and focused on learning outcomes. The results of their finding showed games Improve Student Performance:</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>[icon name=\"icon-quote-left\"] When digital games were compared to other instruction conditions without digital games there was a moderate to strong effect in favor of digital games in terms of broad cognitive competencies... This is equivalent to a 62% success rate in the digital game groups relative to a 50% success rate in the other instruction conditions...\r\n\r\n<strong>This means that the students...in the control group (no game) could have been raised 12% in cognitive learning outcomes if they had received the digital game.</strong> [icon name=\"icon-quote-right\"]</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-bar-chart\"] <span style=\"color: #993300;\">I</span>mprove Student Performance ?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Your students are in the most competitive time in history. The world has become flat. Content is produced all over the world and available instantly to anyone. Students have access to more information than when you grew up and also have more pressure to compete in this global environment. How do you give your student a better chance? Do you know how they compare against the rest of the world? Do you even know how they compare against kids in their classroom today? Class Compete gives your students the opportunity to use technology, creative new testing styles and compete against others in their classroom and the world. Our goal is to increase student performance, and for the first time you will instantly know results and most importantly how they compare. Giving your student a competitive edge is a download away. Try our Free Online Educational Games!</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[button icon=\" icon-user\" size=\"large\" type=\"primary\" value=\" &gt; Join ClassCompete Now! \" title=\"Join/Login ClassCompete\" href=\"http://www.classcompete.com/login\"]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Provide Your Kids with an Advantage in School...Class Compete! [icon name=\"icon-thumbs-up\"]</h2>','PARENTS','','inherit','closed','closed','','348-revision-v1','','','2013-09-06 21:27:16','2013-09-07 01:27:16','',348,'http://www.classcompete.com/348-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
