ote-right\"]</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>[icon name=\"icon-bar-chart\"] <span style=\"color: #993300;\">I</span>mprove Student Performance ?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Your students are in the most competitive time in history. The world has become flat. Content is produced all over the world and available instantly to anyone. Students have access to more information than when you grew up and also have more pressure to compete in this global environment. How do you give your student a better chance? Do you know how they compare against the rest of the world? Do you even know how they compare against kids in their classroom today? Class Compete gives your students the opportunity to use technology, creative new testing styles and compete against others in their classroom and the world. Our goal is to increase student performance, and for the first time you will instantly know results and most importantly how they compare. Giving your student a competitive edge is a download away. Try our Free Online Educational Games!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">[row class=\"row-fluid\"]</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">[col class=\"span3\"]Problem Solving Skills [icon name=\"icon-group\"][/col]</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"color: #993300;\">Encourage Creativity</span> [icon name=\"icon-globe\"][/col]</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">[col class=\"span3\"]Test Prep-Easy for You [icon name=\"icon-check\"][/col]</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">[col class=\"span3\"]<span style=\"color: #993300;\">Happy Kids!</span> <img style=\"border: 0px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-tinymce/addons/emotions/img/popobig/haha.png\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" border=\"0\" />[/col]<br class=\"nc\" />[/row]</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[button icon=\" icon-user\" size=\"large\" type=\"primary\" v